WEBVTT

00:01:59.842 --> 00:02:02.804
it was hard to tell
who the wall was facing,

00:02:02.828 --> 00:02:06.344
because the people living around it
identified as one.

00:02:06.368 --> 00:02:08.135
There was no us and them.

00:02:08.159 --> 00:02:09.516
There was no others.

00:02:09.991 --> 00:02:11.607
During the time of separation,

00:02:11.631 --> 00:02:15.337
both sides developed differently
and formed individual identities.

00:02:15.736 --> 00:02:18.485
All of a sudden, there was
an us and a them.

00:02:18.898 --> 00:02:20.807
A mental wall was built,

00:02:20.831 --> 00:02:24.277
and when the Berlin Wall
fell again in 1989,

00:02:24.301 --> 00:02:27.455
this mental wall in the head
of the people stayed.

00:02:28.033 --> 00:02:32.182
Eastern Germans had to be reintegrated
into their own country,